       Aracnia looked to her lover now, he was trying so hard for her. This 
ment so very much to her, to have someone care so much for her. "Place the 
blue wire in here..." She said, and exposed a small terminal in her right 
hip. "The spark data will transfer into the blank protoform." She said, 
weakly this time as the pain swept over her.
